'From Cuis 3.3 of 2 June 2011 [latest update: #1024] on 30 September 2011 at 3:46:04 pm'!!Editor methodsFor: 'new selection' stamp: 'jmv 9/30/2011 15:10'!selectWord	"Select delimited text or word--the result of double-clicking.""	^self selectWordLeftDelimiters: String cr rightDelimiters: String cr"	"Disable 'double click selects paragraph' in non-Smalltalk editors"	^self selectWordLeftDelimiters: '' rightDelimiters: ''! !!ScrollPane methodsFor: 'event handling' stamp: 'jmv 9/30/2011 15:42'!mouseDown: event	event mouseButton2Pressed  "First check for option (menu) click"		ifTrue: [^ self mouseButton2Activity].	"If pane is not full, pass the event to the last submorph,	assuming it is the most appropriate recipient (!!)"	scroller hasSubmorphs ifTrue: [		scroller submorphs last mouseDown:			(event internalizedTo: scroller from: self)].	event hand 		waitForClicksOrDragOrSimulatedMouseButton2: self		event: event		clkSel: nil		dblClkSel: #doubleClick:		tripleClkSel: #tripleClick:! !!ScrollPane methodsFor: 'event handling' stamp: 'jmv 9/30/2011 15:41'!tripleClick: evt	"Some subclasses might do something"! !!TextEditor methodsFor: 'events' stamp: 'jmv 9/30/2011 15:13'!doubleClick: evt	self selectWord! !!TextEditor methodsFor: 'events' stamp: 'jmv 9/30/2011 15:16'!tripleClick: evt	| here b interval |	b _ paragraph characterBlockAtPoint: evt position.	here _ b stringIndex.	interval _ self privateCurrentString encompassParagraph: (here to: here).	self selectFrom: interval first to: interval last! !!SmalltalkEditor methodsFor: 'events' stamp: 'jmv 9/30/2011 15:12'!doubleClick: evt	| here |	here _ self pointIndex.	(here between: 2 and: model textSize)		ifTrue: [ self selectWord ]		ifFalse: [			"if at beginning or end, select entire string"			self selectAll ]! !!TextModelMorph methodsFor: 'event handling' stamp: 'jmv 9/30/2011 15:42'!tripleClick: event	textMorph tripleClick: event! !!SmalltalkEditor reorganize!('editing keys' browseIt: doIt: exploreIt: fileItIn: implementorsOfIt: inspectIt: pasteInitials: printIt: referencesToIt: save: sendersOfIt:)('do-its' compileSelectionFor:in: debug:receiver:in: debugIt doIt evaluateSelectionAndDo:ifFail: exploreIt inspectIt printIt)('menu messages' browseClassFromIt browseIt classCommentsContainingIt explain fileItIn implementorsOfIt methodSourceContainingIt methodStringsContainingit referencesToIt selectedSelector selectedSymbol sendersOfIt)('typing/selecting keys' argAdvance: crWithIndent: displayIfFalse: displayIfTrue:)('explain' explainAnySel: explainChar: explainClass: explainCtxt: explainGlobal: explainInst: explainMySel: explainNumber: explainPartSel: explainScan: explainTemp:)('new selection' nextTokenFrom:direction: notify:at:in: selectPrecedingIdentifier selectWord)('private' codeProvider explainDelimitor:)('accessing-selection' selection)('events' doubleClick:)!